data.description: WELCOME HOME to this absolutely stunning property on a quiet cul-de-sac in the Bluffs.  Space is plentiful in this 4 bed/2.5 bath with both formal and informal dining as well as an additional space for an office upstairs.  The owners have taken great pride in updating this home.  It is adorned with wood laminate floors, granite countertops, plantation shutters, a beautiful statement wall in the formal dining area, updated light fixtures, lots of natural light, a fireplace, spacious secondary bedrooms as well as a large primary room and ensuite downstairs.  The curb appeal is grand with mature trees in an established neighborhood.  Enjoy family and friends in the beautifully landscaped backyard with a covered patio and additional space for all to enjoy!  Storage is plentiful throughout the home in addition to storage in the two-car garage and shed in the backyard.  Enjoy additional parking on the long driveway and the convenience of the location near HEB, local eateries and shopping!
